aliveandwell.tip.info0: ，Once a day "Luosha City" self-examination self-enlightenment, refresh the mind！！
aliveandwell.tip.info1: ->罗刹国向东两万六千里，过七冲越焦海三寸的黄泥地<-
aliveandwell.tip.info2: ->只为那有一条一丘河，河水流过苟苟营<-
aliveandwell.tip.info3: ->苟苟营当家的叉杆儿唤作马户，十里花场有浑名<-
aliveandwell.tip.info4: ->她两耳傍肩三孔鼻，未曾开言先转腚<-
aliveandwell.tip.info5: ->每一日蹲窝里把蛋来卧，老粉嘴多半辈儿以为自己是只鸡<-
aliveandwell.tip.info6: ->那马户不知道他是一头驴，那又鸟不知道他是一只鸡<-
aliveandwell.tip.info7: ->勾栏从来扮高雅，自古公公好威名<-
aliveandwell.tip.info8: ->打西边来了一个小伙儿他叫马骥，美丰姿 少倜傥 华夏的子弟<-
aliveandwell.tip.info9: ->只为他人海泛舟搏风打浪，龙游险滩流落恶地<-
aliveandwell.tip.info10: ->他见这罗刹国里常颠倒，马户爱听那又鸟的曲<-
aliveandwell.tip.info11: ->三更的草鸡打鸣当司晨，半扇门楣上裱真情<-
aliveandwell.tip.info12: ->它红描翅那个黑画皮，绿绣鸡冠金镶蹄<-
aliveandwell.tip.info13: ->可是那从来煤蛋儿生来就黑，不管你咋样洗呀那也是个脏东西<-
aliveandwell.tip.info14: ->那马户不知道他是一头驴，那又鸟不知道他是一只鸡<-
aliveandwell.tip.info15: ->岂有画堂登猪狗，哪来鞋拔作如意<-
aliveandwell.tip.info16: ->它红描翅那个黑画皮，绿绣鸡冠金镶蹄<-
aliveandwell.tip.info17: ->可是那从来煤蛋儿生来就黑，不管你咋样洗呀那也是个脏东西<-
aliveandwell.tip.info18: ->爱字有心心有好歹，百样爱也有千样的坏<-
aliveandwell.tip.info19: ->女子为好非全都好，还有黄蜂尾上针<-
aliveandwell.tip.info20: ->西边的欧钢有老板，生儿维特根斯坦<-
aliveandwell.tip.info21: ->他言说马户驴又鸟鸡，到底那马户是驴还是驴是又鸟鸡<-
aliveandwell.tip.info22: ->那驴是鸡那个鸡是驴，那鸡是驴那个驴是鸡<-
aliveandwell.tip.info23: ->那马户又鸟，是我们人类根本的问题<-
aliveandwell.tip.infotip1: Bad kid: Steve, time for water!
aliveandwell.tip.infotip2: Steve: The nuclear water made me sick and throw up!
aliveandwell.tip.infotip3: Dangerous world still dangerous? It's hard to survive, isn't it? !
aliveandwell.tip.infotip4: Life and death are determined by fate, wealth and wealth are in heaven!
aliveandwell.tip.infotip5: Tips: Can't get through the night in bed? Just get up once.
aliveandwell.tip.infotip7: Tips: Can't get through the night in bed? Just get up once.
aliveandwell.tip.infotip8: Tip: Nothing to do? There's a book in the top left corner of the backpack bar. Open it.
aliveandwell.tip.infotip9: Tip: Entering the world of Dead Cells (the cage of the imprisoned) without obtaining the Meta-Energy achievement increases negative buffs.
aliveandwell.tip.infotip10: Tips: Do not generate buildings in the first 32 days, do not pre-generate blocks or large-scale map, which will affect the subsequent building generation.
aliveandwell.tip.infotip11: Tips: It is impossible to place blocks such as doors under water, and the digging speed is reduced.
aliveandwell.tip.infotip12: Warning: Early twilight is also dangerous. Don't challenge a dead cell boss until you're sure.
aliveandwell.tip.infotip13: Tips: Can't type? That means you've been infected with a parasite.
aliveandwell.tip.infotip14: Tips: Can't the amount of blood in bed be restored? Due to compatibility issues with the two blood mods, it's good to die once.
aliveandwell.tip.infotip15: Note: Every 32 days the animal will refresh.
aliveandwell.tip.infotip16: Warm tip: Coolie fear will start to generate after 16 days.
aliveandwell.tip.infotip17: Tips: Enchantment requires alchemy levels 5, 8 and 11 to unlock 123 enchantment levels respectively.
aliveandwell.tip.infotip18: Tips: Iron pick above grade pick right click obsidian can be dug.
aliveandwell.tip.infotip19: Make friends and keep your promises!
aliveandwell.tip.infotip20: The gentleman is easy of mind, while the small man is always full of anxiety！
aliveandwell.tip.infotip21: To unlock and generate villagers, you must obtain the achievement of "Nether Fortress"!
aliveandwell.tip.infotip22: Birds of a feather flock together, people flock together, and one leaf knows autumn!
